Nginx RTMP Server (nrs)

This is simple builder for nginx with rtmp module, taken from UPG.GR-MEDIA-SERVER project...

nginx ver: mainline 1.11.3
nginx-rtmp module: git master


USAGE: curl -sL https://raw.githubusercontent.com/beginho/Nginx-Media-Server/master/nginx.sh | sudo bash -

Tested with Ubuntu 14.04 Server

